{"tid":2400780,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇亞雷斯馬競生涯17場16球，進球效率超過當年皇馬C羅","createTime":"2021-02-09T08:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T03:53:12.000Z","uid":19552,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"82c167e623c116e88a29379eda8cad762901c189","tid":2400780,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T08:35:46.000Z","msg":"這場比賽蘇亞雷斯是官方的全場最佳，他踢進了兩球，以16顆進球領跑西甲，很有望再拿下西甲金靴。本賽季加盟馬競後，17場西甲聯賽，蘇亞雷斯踢進了16球，這是21世紀以來的進球紀錄，比當年C羅的18場16球還快一點，而據統計，這16顆進球為馬競帶來了12分積分。<br />\n<br />\n目前蘇亞雷斯的16顆進球，高於13顆的梅西3球，蘇亞雷斯賽後談到這場比賽：雖然沒能贏球，但全隊踢得相當努力，我們將繼續朝著目標前進。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FUVS8mxFU_skc2gfaaii4w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MC40NTcxNDI4NTcxNDI5/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/qw.MRYE_OuJbx4bchhOzOw--~B/aD00Njc7dz03MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/no/__80/c696235ccf66e1215b9e5c3a94e2fc54\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FFUVS8mxFU_skc2gfaaii4w--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MC40NTcxNDI4NTcxNDI5%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fqw.MRYE_OuJbx4bchhOzOw--~B%2FaD00Njc7dz03MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fno%2F__80%2Fc696235ccf66e1215b9e5c3a94e2fc54&h=143fdea6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFIT撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea11a56d9c19b878c862e803d764df14bdee6d1","tid":2400780,"uid":53736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T08:38:17.000Z","msg":"用行動證明自己仲係一線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9eba854f162d87855be51d74674d7260f17eeb9","tid":2400780,"uid":74182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82c167e623c116e88a29379eda8cad762901c189","tid":2400780,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":